      "content": "but why can't i just take them at the same time? i mean they're both just sleep aids, right? it feels like if i'm already taking the melatonin and then i hit it with the zolpidem it would just help me sleep deeper instead of being a problem. if i take them both right before bed it would just be more efficient.",
